## A streamlined .NET .gitignore tailored for the Metatron Suite
## Includes protections for Discord tokens, local databases, and GitHub Action outputs.

# --- Standard .NET Build Results ---
[Dd]ebug/
[Dd]ebugPublic/
[Rr]elease/
[Rr]eleases/
x64/
x86/
[Ww][Ii][Nn]32/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]/
[Aa][Rr][Mm]64/
bld/
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
[Ll]og/
[Ll]ogs/

# GitHub Actions Output Directory
out/

# --- TShock & Metatron Specific (Database Safety) ---
# Prevents committing local test databases to the repository
*.sqlite
*.sqlite-shm
*.sqlite-wal
*.db

# --- Sensitive Configuration Files ---
# CRITICAL: These files contain your Discord Bot Token and Webhook URLs.
# Never commit these to a public repository.
Core.json
HeraldConfig.json
Broadcasts/

# --- IDE & Tooling Noise ---
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
.DS_Store

# --- .NET Core & NuGet ---
project.lock.json
project.fragment.lock.json
artifacts/
*.nupkg
*.snupkg

# --- Others ---
~$*
*~
CodeCoverage/
*.binlog
[Tt]est[Rr]esult*/
[Bb]uild[Ll]og.*
*.VisualState.xml
TestResult.xml
nunit-*.xml
